# Implementation Plan: Flutter Client App (ESPHome) - Phase 1

This plan maps out the creation of the Flutter client-side app `ESPHome` inside the [frontend](file:///c:/Users/chaki/Desktop/ESPHome/frontend) directory. The application targets Android and Web platforms with the package name `com.adacode.esphome`. It uses Riverpod for state management, HiveDB for local caching, and implements the Phase 1 UI/UX screens using a premium, modern design language (dark mode, clean card layouts, smooth transitions).

