### Phase 1 Features: UI/UX Layouts

#### [NEW] [splash_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/chaki/Desktop/ESPHome/frontend/lib/features/splash/presentation/splash_screen.dart)
Splash Screen containing:
* Glowing logo animation.
* Checks local state via Riverpod providers to determine redirect path (Wizard -> Login -> Dashboard).

#### [NEW] [setup_wizard_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/chaki/Desktop/ESPHome/frontend/lib/features/setup/presentation/setup_wizard_screen.dart)
A 3-step setup wizard layout:
1. **Welcome Card:** Introducing the system capabilities with graphics.
2. **Connection Config:** UI to configure local gateway discovery parameters or fallback MQTT host details.
3. **Secret Provisioning:** Prompting for the default security token / `api_key` to store in secure storage.

#### [NEW] [login_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/chaki/Desktop/ESPHome/frontend/lib/features/auth/presentation/login_screen.dart)
Login Screen containing:
* Glassmorphic login card.
* Visual forms validation for email/password.
* Loading state overlays for asynchronous operations.

#### [NEW] [dashboard_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/chaki/Desktop/ESPHome/frontend/lib/features/dashboard/presentation/dashboard_screen.dart)
Primary App Dashboard containing:
* Horizontal tabs representing "Rooms" or groups.
* Grid layout of IoT nodes with dynamic status chips (`Local-WS`, `Cloud-MQTT`, `Offline`).
* Live telemetry summary cards (average temperature/humidity).

#### [NEW] [node_control_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/chaki/Desktop/ESPHome/frontend/lib/features/control/presentation/node_control_screen.dart)
GPIO Switch / Load Panel:
* Grid/List of active switches showing toggle indicators.
* Real-time charts or numeric display cards for sensor nodes.

#### [NEW] [settings_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/chaki/Desktop/ESPHome/frontend/lib/features/settings/presentation/settings_screen.dart)
Control parameters and rule customization UI:
* Form fields to create automated trigger conditions (e.g. `If Sensor temperature > 30.0 Fan -> ON`).
* Input fields for rule offset/hysteresis margins to avoid rapid relay oscillations.

