## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
Once project setup is completed, we will execute standard layout analysis tests:
```bash
cd frontend
flutter analyze
flutter test
```

### Manual Verification
1. We will compile the web app to ensure layout compatibility:
   ```bash
   flutter run -d chrome
   ```
2. We will run mock integration tests inside the controllers to verify screen flows (e.g., clicking Next on the wizard successfully transitions to the Login page, and completing Auth enters the Dashboard).
